videos.headline: LSU strikes early with 13-yard TD
videos.description: Joe Burrow finds Ja'Marr Chase for a 13-yard LSU touchdown.

videos.headline: Edwards-Helaire squeezes in for 1-yard TD
videos.description: Clyde Edwards-Helaire pushes through the defenders into the end zone to give LSU a 14-0 lead.

videos.headline: Jefferson's 9-yard TD pass increases LSU's lead
videos.description: Joe Burrow throws to Justin Jefferson for a 9-yard LSU touchdown, making the score 21-0.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Jefferson's 9-yard TD pass increases LSU’s lead) 2019/08/31

videos.headline: Burrow connects with Marshall for 8-yard TD
videos.description: Terrace Marshall Jr. catches Joe Burrow's pass in the end zone to give the Tigers a 28-0 lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Burrow connects with Marshall for 8-yard TD) 2019/08/31

videos.headline: Marshall picks up 2nd TD of the day
videos.description: Terrace Marshall Jr. scores his second touchdown of the game, a 3-yard run and a 35-0 lead..

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Marshall picks up 2nd TD of the day) 2019/08/31 ESHEET

videos.headline: Fournette runs in for short TD
videos.description: Lanard Fournette breaks through the defense for a 2-yard Tigers touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Fournette runs in for short TD) 2019/08/31

videos.headline: Burrow throws 5 TDs, leading LSU to rout in opener
videos.description: LSU quarterback Joe Burrow throws five touchdown passes in the Tigers' 55-3 win vs. Georgia Southern.
